	</facsimile>
	<text>
		<body>
			<div>
				<pb facs="#facs_1" n="1"/>
				<p facs="#facs_1_tr_1">
					<lg>
						<l facs="#facs_1_l_31">[↑] and they seemed to enjoy themselves.</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_l_23">[↑] and frozen fruit and coffee and [?] and sandwiches</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_l_15">[↑] &amp; another young man and girl. I gave them ice cream</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_l">[↑] I had a party with Chipman, Marianne [Horustein?],</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_8">
                            <placeName ref="geo-11524648">Somerville College</placeName>
                        </l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_9">
                            <date when="1949-02-12">12 February</date>
                        </l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_10">My dear <persName ref="gnd-118777378">Raymond</persName>
                        </l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_11">many thanks for your</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_12">letters of <date when="1949-02-03">3rd</date> and <date when="1949-02-08">8th February</date>. I am very</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_13">glad that you get some pleasure out of your</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_14">lectures and that they are a great success,</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_15">though that does not surprise me in the least.</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_16">I sent you the Hobbes letter and the Lieftinck</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_17">photostats on Friday. Yesterday I received</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_18">from <persName ref="gnd-116183853">Miss Bing</persName> photostats of the relevant</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_19">passages in the Galen De Consuetudinibus.</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_20">At my request she has photostated (a)</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_21">the whole fascicule to keep it in the Library</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_22">at our disposal (b) the important pages,</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_23">to be sent to you.</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_24">It is a German.</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_25">translation of the Arabic text. A part from</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_26">the Proclus text which exists only in</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_27">Arabic, there are the two small fragments</l>
						<l facs="#facs_1_tr_1_tl_28">from the Timaeus itself which are from a</l>
					</lg>
				</p>
				<pb facs="#facs_2" n="2"/>
				<p facs="#facs_2_tr_1">
					<lg>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_1">(to the end of the dialogue)</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_2">[gestrichen] context than the one translated by</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_3">Chalcidius and have been preserved in the</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_4">Latin translation of the Galen. I wonder</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_5">whether they should be printed as an</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_6">appendix to the Chalcidius. Or with the</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_7">Cicero? - As to the Berlin Ms., Mrs Bing</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_8">has just had the visit from a woman (Frl. Chr.</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_9">v. Kühn?) who seems an old friend and</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_10">who is in charge of Monuments in Berlin</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_11">("Schlösser und Gärten"). She strickes me as</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_12">a better person to write to than Frau Kirchner.</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_13">I shall arrange that with Bing when I see</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_14">her this week. - Walzer has written to me that</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_16">he has been informed that the MS of the Theologia</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_18">Aristoteles, [the one] used by Dieterici, formerly in Berlin</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_19">is in Tübingin now. It would cost ca. 53 DM</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_20">to have it photostated and he could arrange</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_21">payment through Snell (whose daughter is with</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_22">the Walzers more or less permanently) unless</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_23">the W. I. had German funds for these</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_24">purposes. I had written to Bing inquiring</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_25">about this and to Walzer, asking him</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_26">provisionally whether it would not be possible</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_27">to have microfilms made instead of</l>
						<l facs="#facs_2_tr_1_tl_28">photostats. I hope this was all right.</l>
					</lg>
				</p>
				<pb facs="#facs_3" n="3"/>
				<p facs="#facs_3_tr_2">
					<lg>
						<l facs="#facs_3_tr_2_tl_1">The [Minias?] have a little daughter Margarita</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_tr_2_tl_2">Juan, everything went well, Mother and child</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_tr_2_tl_3">are well and as the child is now a week</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_tr_2_tl_4">old the critical time seems to have passed.</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_l">They are very happy.</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_tr_2_tl_7">He received the first proofes of the Phaedo</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_tr_2_tl_8">a few days after the baby arrived and</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_tr_2_tl_9">was very pleased with them. There is</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_tr_2_tl_10">not a single printing mistake in them he</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_l_13">says. I expect you got a copy? From</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_tr_2_tl_14">what you wrote to me some weeks ago, I gather</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_tr_2_tl_15">that you do not want to read proofs, except</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_tr_2_tl_16">for the last ones? Correct me if I am</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_l_20">wrong. I agreed to look at the proofs</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_tr_2_tl_19">with him. Please let us know if there</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_tr_2_tl_20">is anything which you don't like.</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_tr_2_tl_21">I have written to Sonja about</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_l_56">the Taylor MS. If it is still in my</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_l_28">drawer when I come to London, I shall</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_l_35">send it. I shall be in London on</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_l_42">Tuesday. The Walzer proofs were sent to</l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_l_49">me here. I shall take Mom to the </l>
						<l facs="#facs_3_tr_2_tl_33">institute.</l>
					</lg>
				</p>
				<pb facs="#facs_4" n="4"/>
				<p facs="#facs_4_tr_1">
					<lg>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_1">Minio is going to Italy during the Easter holidayes</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_2">You write about my coming (or not</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_3">coming) to Montreal always in expressions like</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_l">"if you really decided..." or "do not want"</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_6">etc., as if I were a free agent. Believe</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_7">me the temptation to get out of this place,</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_8">especially with the prospect of - for my</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_9">standards - many tutorials, and to go to</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_10">Montreal, (not to speak of the temptation to</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_11">exchange the rissoles and whale steaks against</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_12">barbecue chicken and steaks!) is overwhelming.</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_13">But I really do not see how I can having</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_14">accepted this position, get out of my obligations</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_15">whenever I chose and then come back and take</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_16">what they give me - (even if it is only whale</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_l_13">steak). It is a question of 'Either - Or'.</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_19">As I said, I might be able to take leave</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_20">of absence for the Michaelmas Term. -</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_21">I shall have the apparatus fontium in print</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_22">before I leave.</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_23">All the best,</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_24">Love,</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_26">Yours</l>
						<l facs="#facs_4_tr_1_tl_27">Lotte</l>
					</lg>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
